      "sanskritName": "Pitta",
      "description": {
        "en": "Pitta governs digestion, metabolism, transformation, and body temperature. It is composed of Fire and Water elements.",
        "sa": "पित्तं पाकक्रियां नियन्त्रयति।",
        "zh-Hant": "主司消化、代謝、轉化及體溫，由火與水元素組成",
